{"tid":1263730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大阪即時】堅持越洋請願 陳浩天家人收恐嚇電話","createTime":"2019-06-28T10:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T01:59:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":85,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"16615a80d6b5dea43f86886202996be81625ef25","tid":1263730,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"【大阪即時】堅持越洋請願 陳浩天家人收恐嚇電話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/13x7h9hM/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F13x7h9hM%2Fimage.jpg&h=dbad7e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天在Justice20（J20） 英語記者會中表示，家人近日收到恐嚇電話，致電者承認行為針對陳浩天越洋請願。陳在記者會問答環節中表示事件令自己承受額外壓力，家人亦有曾力勸他取消行程。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天日前到日本大阪G20請願，希望喚醒國際社會關注香港現況，並要求各國向中國政府施壓。是次請願行動不乏支持者，有多名在日港人響應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/m2LSW-ttb/BANNER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fm2LSW-ttb%2FBANNER.jpg&h=71c11b9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97d37b6c347a3a6a30abe2f2b36527acaaaf390d","tid":1263730,"uid":30063,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"不論你地認唔認同陳浩天，佢的確為香港付出咗好多，唔好再屌佢係鬼啦，呢個時候唔好分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322d373185f5d1a7b5ee5c6bb95bb89bc326cbaa","tid":1263730,"uid":61281,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HKVDC_2017 #79563！<br />\n極可疑五毛行為人士！<br />\n專扮本土獨派 力屌泛民左膠<br />\n！！大家睇路！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/28/183643_0d28fedbe902915eb9c4dd2df57a2725.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F28%2F183643_0d28fedbe902915eb9c4dd2df57a2725.png&h=f56d1d7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc76ab244f7cb963167ab4bc85a94f73f348c643","tid":1263730,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":5,"scor